   387→                <li><a href="./docs/ChebyshevCircles/PolynomialProperties.html" style="color: #3498db;">PolynomialProperties</a> (130 lines) - Polynomial degree and coefficient properties</li>
   388→                <li><a href="./docs/ChebyshevCircles/PowerSumEquality.html" style="color: #3498db;">PowerSumEquality</a> (273 lines) - General power sum equality</li>
   389→                <li><a href="./docs/ChebyshevCircles/ChebyshevOrthogonality.html" style="color: #3498db;">ChebyshevOrthogonality</a> (538 lines) - Discrete orthogonality relations</li>
   390→                <li><a href="./docs/ChebyshevCircles/MainTheorem.html" style="color: #3498db;">MainTheorem</a> (473 lines) - Main theorem and supporting results</li>
   391→            </ul>
   392→
   393→            <h3>Quick Links to Major Results</h3>
